{"step": 65, "message": "{\n  \"chosen_product\": {\n    \"product_url\": \"https://www.rei.com/product/246731/keen-hightrail-mid-waterproof-hiking-boots-mens\",\n    \"product_name\": \"KEEN Hightrail Mid Waterproof Hiking Boots - Men's\"\n  },\n  \"extracted_attributes\": {\n    \"price\": 160,\n    \"weight_oz\": 29.3,\n    \"waterproof\": true,\n    \"height_category\": \"mid\",\n    \"rating\": 4.6,\n    \"review_count\": 181\n  },\n  \"cart_added\": {\n    \"size\": \"10.5\",\n    \"quantity\": 1,\n    \"in_stock_at_add\": true\n  },\n  \"reasoning\": \"Narrowed to men's waterproof mid hiking boots under $250 with size 10.5 available, then sorted by customer rating. The two higher-rated results had fewer than 100 reviews, while this KEEN Hightrail had 181 reviews, a 4.6 rating, waterproof KEEN.DRY membrane, mid/over-the-ankle support, and a 1 lb. 13.3 oz. pair weight under 40 oz. Size 10.5 was selectable and in stock, and one pair was added to the cart.\"\n}", "terminal": true}
